@node Top
@top midi-ble-rt

midi-ble-rt bridges ALSA Sequencer MIDI ports to configured BLE-MIDI devices
through BlueZ GATT.  The public programs are @command{midi-ble-rtd}, the daemon,
and @command{midi-ble-rtctl}, the control and diagnostics CLI.

@menu
